{"tid":727529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【泰洞救少足】救人英國專家曾破最深潛紀錄 「恐慌喺洞穴潛水無用」","createTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T06:28:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f44868b84ca355660d596f8da5db304bc41cac54","tid":727529,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"「你們有多少人？13個？太好了。」泰國一隊少年足球隊及教練在清萊美賽縣山洞區失蹤逾一周後尋回，全部生還。找到他們的是2名經驗豐富的英國蛙人，曾在世界多國參與類似搜救工作，今次應泰方請求參與搜索。<br />\n<br />\n56歲的斯坦頓（Rick Stanton）及47歲的沃蘭特（John Volanthen）並非全職蛙人，斯坦頓當了消防員近25年，沃蘭特就是位網絡工程師。兩人同屬英國一個洞穴救援組織的成員，過去合作多年甚有默契，2011年8月更一同創下洞穴潛水最深的世界紀錄，在西班牙一個名為「Pozo Azul」的洞穴深潛9公里。<br />\n<br />\n兩人2010年到法國協助拯救一名被困的潛水員，最後在距離洞口780米發現屍體，他們2012年獲皇室頒獎章表揚為搜救出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n斯坦頓兒時看有關潛水的節目後產生興趣，讀大學時加入洞穴探險和潛水學會，2004年曾到墨西哥協助搜救13名英國洞穴探險者，至2012年獲頒授員佐勳章（MBE）。<br />\n<br />\n沃蘭特就是當童軍時開始洞穴探險，他指洞穴搜救工作需要清晰頭腦，又指若應對得宜就沒有危險，「恐慌和腎上腺素在某些情況很好用，但並非用在洞穴潛水上&hellip;&hellip;如果做得正確，就不會有危險」。<br />\n<br />\n從泰國當局發放的影片看到，兩人找到失蹤者時立即安慰他們「會有更多人來」，有人表示很高興獲救，一把英式口音回應：「我們也很高興。」有人問他們來自何處，二人就回答「英國」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/135234_1c9175afab673b54337aab161ca9659e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F135234_1c9175afab673b54337aab161ca9659e.png&h=68071774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斯坦頓（左）沃蘭特（右）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180703/58393019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F58393019&d=Nyti4CReHsaybVxJJYr7HJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=05364e08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F58393019&h=7533538a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180703/58393019</a>"},{"pid":"71defbee601c55fea65bf883dbc207e6021daef9","tid":727529,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244565e8f9eb085aa8f20ac2856fad15e91d67c5","tid":727529,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c432230b5abd25360a66c5144e45b92720e4443d","tid":727529,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"it狗都可以咁多技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d396f3e9d62434de02f1f2a20049e20d3ad1ae","tid":727529,"uid":140454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c432230b5abd25360a66c5144e45b92720e4443d","tid":727529,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:55:16.000Z","msg":"it狗都可以咁多技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"IT洛威拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ca120e2d8f539b34f9f01f9e3d30de8bf53574","tid":727529,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"留名睇有人入黎逐個負皮+屌人含英國撚"},{"pid":"49596fc9383ddc297385a57ee6cb0fc0a4f7c488","tid":727529,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"推post"}]}